# python function in/out logger

## Install

Requires Python 3

### Using pip

```
pip3 install loggit -U
```

### Using pipenv

```
pipenv install loggit
```

## Usage

### Simple monitoring

```python
from loggit import log

@log
def myfunc(*args, **kwargs):
    ...
    return result
```
